sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Sales Rep<br/>(screen flow user)
    participant F as Screen Flow<br/>Deal Desk Currency Checker
    participant H as HTTP Callout Action<br/>(the one you built, no code)
    participant N as Named Credential<br/>Engine
    participant A as Frankfurter API<br/>api.frankfurter.dev

    U->>F: Enters amount: 50000 (USD)
    F->>H: Run action — amount=50000,<br/>base=USD, symbols=EUR
    H->>N: GET callout:Frankfurter/v1/latest?…
    N->>A: Request (no auth needed —<br/>the credential just holds the URL)
    A-->>N: { "amount": 50000.0, "base": "USD",<br/>"date": "…", "rates": { "EUR": 43733 } }
    N-->>H: 200 OK
    H-->>F: Typed output — drill into<br/>2XX → rates → EUR
    F-->>U: Screen shows: "≈ €43,733 today"

    Note over U,A: A real integration, built entirely<br/>with clicks — the OAuth modules made this trivial
